{"tid":626821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路政署署長鍾錦華：不存在未有施工圖就施工","createTime":"2018-04-12T12:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T12:23:26.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"300382e433422f1b084241f3d1d20d5032c153bd","tid":626821,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:23:26.000Z","msg":"路政署署長鍾錦華，否認港珠澳大橋人工島未有施工圖就開始施工。<br />\n<br />\n他澄清整條大橋的施工圖是逐步審批，上次記者會他提及的2014年核准施工圖，是指隧道與人工島接合的部分，而早在2013年開工安放扭工字塊的，是人工島另一邊、與大橋接駁的部分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/831453417046728/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F831453417046728%2F&d=%2BI%2BMj8jsIKeOGRJVcOuxUsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=4eb79680\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/831453417046728/</a>"}]}